    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "could you elaborate on the \"biological differences\" you mentioned? i've seen some controversial papers online discussing genetic markers or evolutionary psychology explanations for these behavioral trends. is there any serious academic weight to those arguments in the context of crime?",
